    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban employers from making deductions shortfalls from pay for retail workers",
        "additional_details": "We believe these deductions are unfair, and should not be allowed.\r\n \r\nMany households are struggling with the cost of living, and deductions from pay can exacerbate this. Deductions from pay can also affect benefit entitlements, creating further financial difficulties.\r\n",
        "background": "Protect workers and their families by banning employers from reducing pay by up to 10%, if there are shortfalls, such as stock or till shortages.",
